    experiment(adminroute): INSUFFICIENT_STATIONS silent-acceptance mutant for MIST trace-oracle demo
    
    Deliberately ACCEPT insufficient-station routes (Response 1 -> HTTP 200) instead of rejecting (Response 0 + faultName -> HTTP 400), turning INSUFFICIENT_STATIONS_FAULT (one of the 10 tracked faults) into a silent-acceptance bug. Lets MIST's intent-aware trace oracle (SilentAcceptanceInvariant) be demonstrated catching what status/fault-name oracles miss. Other validations unchanged. Revert to restore correct rejection.

